                  Join Telegram
                </a>
                <a href="#newsletter" class="flex items-center text-primary hover:underline">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M1.5 8.67v8.58a3 3 0 003 3h15a3 3 0 003-3V8.67l-8.928 5.493a3 3 0 01-3.144 0L1.5 8.67z"></path><path d="M22.5 6.908V6.75a3 3 0 00-3-3h-15a3 3 0 00-3 3v.158l9.714 5.978a1.5 1.5 0 001.572 0L22.5 6.908z"></path></svg>
                  Join Mailing List
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card bg-background border border-primary p-6 rounded-lg">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Contribute</h3>
